"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640629382,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"HVSs_hp-vfvLZom6LVkKkPnvUy9o2kD8ooC3-9cD49E\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6d7D2522819468b1CCf46c5BFeB3d05b657003Ca\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c_N_plJXdlmshyhpiNsRjZW4zz9m_JD8xSWWaDPyl2c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"XAkcUi0TQF95FPG5XXExS5u6kMHLTIRHKaDXqPsCGaE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Q0P-55WQe2HsyMj0OEDoTnbgnjvBboqkW5lO1vJaJOJX7m0y9Xom_HXPTG_BPDjzLO8URvH04U2tSR3W1wXxtg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4ef3ee6d35080d75aecb05255f0ba3bf9b1898097c45fd8ef73d0b03eb151e0c75ac1d64565049f1716338665854f915eca3a54f848e6d7510bde5c7379f9e3f1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"c_N_plJXdlmshyhpiNsRjZW4zz9m_JD8xSWWaDPyl2c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"XAkcUi0TQF95FPG5XXExS5u6kMHLTIRHKaDXqPsCGaE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi